name: Youth Beginner
description: Youth Beginner - This learn-to-swim program will teach participants the fundamental movement skills for the 4 strokes and learn useful entries including dives and rolls. Youth Intermediate - Provides youth with the intermediate skills to perform the strokes of their choice; freestyle, backstroke, breaststroke and butterfly.
